 簽收一份交出文件令，要唔知幾多日內交出文件"},{"pid":"268cb0fbe8ddb4ce839699ee7ef4e010145c850f","tid":2355034,"uid":219128,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c3b38eb1a0d5f028d7d499860ee066bca5657245","tid":2355034,"uid":165028,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:45:20.000Z","msg":"點解佢地要咁深黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"會員 #165028 - 何東精神（團結）<br />\n，前稱純正港人(港豬)，離地中產，天安門旅遊，Frizzle(港豬)，Alexander(離地)極有可能係五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍, 請大家多加注意!<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n#1 - 周街都貼連豬搞到心都煩哂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n睇見隻豬就火滾想撕左佢<br />\n<br />\n#1 - 誠哥真係好醒目<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n開金口講句要對年青人網開一面<br />\n而家旗下百佳, 豐澤等避開一劫<br />\n如果唔係被暴徒燒毀打爛唔知幾多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家見到黑衫蒙面阻住我架車都唔出聲屌佢地<br />\n作狀支持佢地俾個like 等佢地放行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1 - 想同琴晚太子站嘅一個勇武道歉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n因為我當時太驚又怕死<br />\n所以同其他乘客撞你出門口<br />\n希望你無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1 - 好怕d勇武派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n街上面見到佢地都會避之則吉<br />\n怕會招惹埋d警察<br />\n琴日黃大仙站成班又面罩又防具咁衝入車廂<br />\n嚇到我下個站即刻落車<br />\n<br />\n#1 - （求屌醒）一直唔明白你地搞抗爭做咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n我80後 本身都係中產階級 收入穩定又係專業人士<br />\n雖然近呢個月都聽左好多理據話要爭取好多野<br />\n包括撤回逃犯條例 調整警權過大 之類<br />\n但係我就唔明點解一定要搞到武力衝突先收手<br />\n再加上止舉令警民官民矛盾越來越大 對香港真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁多野 真心唔明每個星期搞一兩單衝突暴動真係好咩 已經港九新界都搞砸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1 - 想報仇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767121</a><br />\n<br />\n[quote]發現女朋友個WhatsApp 有同第二個男仔有纏綿對話<br />\n我知道個男仔有參加社會又搞衝擊<br />\n宜家想搞佢罪証再報警篤灰"},{"pid":"fdf721795bfad7d5d1e7011eb8cf3cc63d89210d","tid":2355034,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:51:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97cc42e2ee1e132fcd4c3bce12a0e2e81c1dedc7","tid":2355034,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:51:25.000Z","msg":"黑警屌你老母"},{"pid":"01742fc7ce2c48fb7db09335c1d6877568d3ade5","tid":2355034,"uid":94069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a91166f2daa56ed5c1a9acfa62c298122ee5da","tid":2355034,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664dcb400ac03572351db0f6a8f7bc73a03ebd02","tid":2355034,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T01:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F44SXy6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF44SXy6.png&h=158ad8ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d0794d168bd3bbb0c1a35cd362b7833ad3b64eb","tid":2355034,"uid":54291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc